import React, { Component } from 'react'; import './recommended-exercise.css' const emojiStyle = { fontSize: 100, color: "red", } export default class Planks extends Component { render() { return (

Planks









Description:

Arrange yourself as if you are doing a push-up.

Rise to the top of this position, ensuring your back is completely straight, and hold this position.



Note ❗

  • Make sure your elbows are directly under your shoulders
  • Line your wrists up with your elbows
  • Push your body upwards, and keep your chin tight to your neck



    • Benefits:

  • Improve your posture
  • Boost muscle definition in shoulders, chest, legs and back
  • Increase flexibility
  • Reduce risk of injury in back and spinal column and get rid of back pain
  • Boost metabolism



    • Recommended

    Speed/Duration:

    Beginner: Start with 30 seconds every day and add five to 10 minutes to your sessions in each subsequent week.

    Intermediate: Complete at least 30 minutes of biking every day. Try to cycle at the speed of 16-19km per hour.

    ) } }
